Ma femme, Peggy.

629
00:53:17,211 --> 00:53:19,588
Enchantée et félicitations.

630
00:53:19,755 --> 00:53:21,048
Freddie Quell.

631
00:53:24,218 --> 00:53:25,803
Ma fille, Elizabeth.

